title: Debbery 12PCS Replacement Nail Polish Brush Kit, with Handle Dip Powder Liquid Replacement Brushes, Disposable Nail Varnish Brushes, for Gel Manicure Dip Powder, Home Salon Dip Powder
features: Package includes: The replacement nail polish brush kit contains 12 brushes, which is enough to meet your daily needs and reduce cleaning time (nail polish is not included)

Suitable size: Each nail polish brush is about 4.5 cm long and 1.1 cm wide, which is suitable for dipping nail polish, or for dipping powder base coat and top coat; please pay attention to measure the size of the nail polish bottle before purchase to ensure the right size
Premium material: The disposable nail varnish brushes is made of plastic material, the handle is sturdy and durable, and the bristles are soft and not easy to fall off, harden or knot
Easy to replace: When you want to replace the nail varnish brush, just open the nail polish bottle, take out the old applicator brush, insert the new brush and twist it off

Wide range of uses: The replacement nail polish brush kit set is suitable for home and nail salon use, for manicure, gel polish nail design, fine painting, drawing flower and pattern designs on nails, adding glitter, etc
description: Product description Product name: 12 replacement nail polish brush kit Size: 1.8 inches (46 mm) long Color: black brush head + white handle Warm Tips: If the bristles are bent or hardened, soak them in hot water and they will return to normal When using disposable nail varnish brushes, to prevent the brush from hardening, wait 10-15 seconds after applying the dip nail activator before applying the dip nail polish. Safety Warning For external use only
